      <h1 class="mb-2">We Are Ember Experts</h1>
      <div class="split-content__wrapper">
        <div class="split-content__content m-0">
          <p class="medium">
            Mainmatter has been actively involved in shaping Ember for years.
            We’re behind <a href="/ember-initiative/" class="link-black">The Ember Initiative</a> that supports the Ember ecosystem.
            We also maintain key add-ons such as  <a href="https://ember-simple-auth.com/" class="link-black">Ember Simple Auth</a>, <a href="http://qunit-dom.com/" class="link-black">QUnit Dom</a>, and <a href="https://ember-test-selectors.com" class="link-black">Ember Test Selectors</a>. 
          </p>
          <p class="medium">
            Our team includes many experienced engineers, including Chris Manson (Ember Core Team member, 
